'''Gentle Giant Studios''' is a company that specializes in scanning, digital modeling, and sculpting. They were present on the set of [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|Episode II]], where they digitally scanned a number of props for posterity.

'''Gentle Giant''' produces and sells a popular line of exclusive ''Star Wars''-themed sculptures and character busts.

